    "WANDiffusionModel composes T2VModelConfig (config)",
    "WANDiffusionModel depends_on FlowUniPCMultistepScheduler (sample_scheduler)",
    "WANDiffusionModel depends_on RectifiedFlow (rectified_flow)",
    "WANDiffusionModel depends_on BaseVAE (tokenizer)",
    "WANDiffusionModel depends_on FastEmaModelUpdater / DTensorFastEmaModelUpdater (net_ema_worker)",
    "WANDiffusionModel depends_on peft.LoraConfig / inject_adapter_in_model (optional LoRA injection)",
    "Lyra2Model composes Lyra2T2VConfig (overrides config type)",
    "Lyra2Model depends_on Sparse3DCache (spatial memory)",
    "Lyra2Model depends_on T2VCondition (condition dataclass from modules.conditioner)"
  ],

  "inheritance_chain": "torch.nn.Module -> ImaginaireModel -> WANDiffusionModel -> Lyra2Model",

  "config_inheritance_chain": "T2VModelConfig -> Lyra2T2VConfig",

  "important_notes": [
    "ImaginaireModel is the abstract base: training_step, validation_step, forward are NotImplementedError",
    "WANDiffusionModel provides full diffusion training/inference; forward() is effectively a pass (deferred to net)",
    "Lyra2Model adds AR (autoregressive) framepack-based spatial memory and multi-buffer slots on top of WANDiffusionModel",
    "T2VModelConfig uses attrs.define; Lyra2T2VConfig adds ~30 extra fields for spatial AR, self-augmentation, and memory",
    "EMAConfig and I4LoraConfig are attrs dataclasses composed inside T2VModelConfig",
    "LoRA injection (peft) is optional and guarded by I4LoraConfig.enabled; peft import is wrapped in try/except",
    "FSDP (fully_shard) support is conditional on fsdp_shard_size > 1",
    "build_net() uses lazy_instantiate with meta-device init then broadcasts DTensor model states",
    "set_up_model() creates both self.net and optional self.net_ema using build_net()",
    "training_step in WANDiffusionModel: get_data_and_condition -> rectified_flow noise -> net forward -> MSE loss",
    "Lyra2Model overrides training_step, generate_samples_from_batch, and decode with spatial AR logic",
    "Sparse3DCache is a helper class in lyra2_model.py for 3D spatial correspondence caching",
    "WAN2PT1_I2V_COND_LATENT_KEY constant used for I2V conditioning latent key"
  ]
}
